Package: allotaxonometR
Type: Package
Title: R impelementation of ideas from 'Allotaxonometry and rank-turbulence divergence: A universal instrument for comparing complex systems' by Peter Sheridan Dodds, and others
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stephen Charlesworth
Maintainer: Stephen Charlesworth <mistasteve@gmail.com>
Description: Tool for evaluating changes in complex systems by examining changes in rankings of the components over time (examples, baby names, words on Twitter, NBA point total rankings.)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: tidyverse
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat
